criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Portuguese as their first language;

          -  minimum of eight years of formal education;

          -  normal vision or corrected to normal and normal hearing;

          -  no prior experience with meditation;

          -  patients should be taking stable doses of methylphenidate (for at least a month) for
             their disorder as prescribed by their doctors.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with neurological and psychiatric disorders such as psychosis,
             obsessive-compulsive disorder or Tourette's syndrome.
